# Query Validation Agent — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A full **Query Validation Agent** (architecture §2.6) replacing the basic [SQOValidator](file:///c:/HelioX/tests/test_query_analyzer.py#340-412) stub. The agent detects problems, **corrects** the SQO when possible, and locks it only when checks pass.

